snippet.textDisplay:
Hrithik Roshan er, "Mission Kashmir" Cinema er 1ta gaan ache, "Rind Posh maal".. Otar lyric ta koto ta realistic, aj ei gaan ta sunle bojha jai... Ami lyric ta dicchi
 "Sangeet ko naa roke deewar
Sangeet jaaye sarhad ke paar
Ho sangeet maane naa dharm jaat
Sangeet se judi kaaynaat
Sangeet ki naa koi zubaan
Sangeet mein hai geeta quraan
Sangeet mein hai allah o raam
Sangeet mein hai duniya tamaam"

Gaan kono dhormo, bera mane na, shilpo k kokhono dhormo, bera die atkano jai na... Etai tar proman.. Bangladesh er gaan gulo sune mon vore jai just.. ❤... Sotti bolte erai bangla ta k somman die bachiye rakhche
